Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.39,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.3\fs12\c&H1D251A&\frz343\pos(499.5,110.5)\fax0.1}Commuter IC supported here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:07.88,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:10.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Summer's in full swing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:11.72,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Very much so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:14.91,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I think we're almost at Gotoh-san's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:18.39,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for showing me around, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.43,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all! I'm really \Nlooking forward to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:23.41,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It'll be such a new experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:27.23,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we mainly only get \Ntogether at Starry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:28.58,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:31.71,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Gotoh-san's house is like!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:37.43,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She said something about a cramped \Ncardboard box reminding her of home...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.19,0:00:40.18,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A house like a cardboard box?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:43.79,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan says the funniest things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:45.32,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:46.88,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Neither can I!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:49.82,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some sweets and a movie I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:52.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You didn't forget why \Nwe're doing this, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.30,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,No, I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:57.37,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We're designing T-shirts \Nfor our concert, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:00:58.39,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:00.76,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Ryo-senpai could've come too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:02.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I did invite her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:05.55,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She says her grandma\Ntook a turn for the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:07.60,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Is she all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:09.17,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:12.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,This is like the tenth critical time \Nfor her grandma this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.28,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way the guitar comes in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.55,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:19.65,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, at least her grandma really exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:21.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's a heckuva low bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.67,DefaultTop,Mob F/K,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hang out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:25.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Once, when some classmates invited \Nher to hang out with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:28.60,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my dog Pe'z has to have surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:29.56,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(359,1)\blur0.3\fs16\fnComic Sans MS\b0\c&H593052&\pos(367.5,62)}sob sob sob
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:29.56,Default,Mob F/K,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:32.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So she said, but she's never even had a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:33.98,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:35.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:39.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's "I just got a call from \Nmy twin sister separated at birth,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:41.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and "my dad was in a car crash, \Nand now he has amnesia."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Just all the silliest excuses...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:47.71,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed by how easily she comes up \Nwith such a wide range of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:49.96,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.26,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I love me a bad girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:54.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's a serious Ryo obsession right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.06,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We're here! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:03.51,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\an8\fnArial Black\c&H565350&\3c&HEEEEEC&}Welcome!  Members of Kessoku Band\N{\fs15}We Hope Your Time Here Heals You in Both Mind and Body
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:25.04,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx50\fscy50\bord2\an8\fnArial Black\c&H565350&\3c&HEEEEEC&\pos(321.5,95.5)}Welcome!  Members of Kessoku Band\N{\fs15}We Hope Your Time Here Heals You in Both Mind and Body
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:11.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,This... is it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:15.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It... does say "Kessoku Band," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:18.08,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Did she mention her house was a ryokan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:22.33,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. It just looks like \Na normal house to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.88,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:29.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.53,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:33.15,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.42,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord2\fs14\fnTimes New Roman\c&H454133&\3c&HABA19D&\pos(317,213.5)}Sergeant For a Day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.99,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yaaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:44.14,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.46,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked dark, cramped spaces,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.83,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd bury my face deep in my hood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.21,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes resented the heartless world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:09.96,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,but yearned for love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.60,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked being soaked by the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.97,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,because my face looked better clouded over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.61,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended to be afraid of the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.44,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,while waiting for the sky to burst
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:31.40,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum through the light's distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:35.82,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make thunder roar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:41.62,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum beyond the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:45.75,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:51.81,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum in a harmonizing quartet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:55.80,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cause a revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:04:01.81,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum in a lamenting forte
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:06.56,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.86,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&H9756DB&\fnImpact\fs30\pos(238.5,132.5)}BOCCHI THE ROCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.86,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&H9756DB&\fnComic Sans MS\fs26\b1\pos(415,248)}#07 To Your House
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:38.17,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,184)\an8\bord2\fs14\fnTimes New Roman\c&H454133&\3c&HABA19D&\pos(316.5,80.5)}Sergeant For a Day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.21,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having fun, Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:31.34,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I b-b-bombed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.05,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:38.03,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san's made it clear how much \Nshe's been looking forward to this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:41.39,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-san knows the kindest words \Nto soothe my bombed soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.22,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.42,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:47.85,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx50\fscy50\bord2\an8\fnArial Black\c&H565350&\3c&HEEEEEC&\pos(321.5,95.5)}Welcome!  Members of Kessoku Band\N{\fs15}We Hope Your Time Here Heals You in Both Mind and Body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:45.96,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.10,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san, these are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.87,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy them with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.20,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:05:00.11,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, t-trendiness emanates from the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:05:01.61,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(479,1)\blur0.3\fs14\fnComic Sans MS\c&H97E0CC&\3c&HDAFFF1&\b0\frz351.1\pos(311.5,57)}shining
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:05:01.61,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(479,1)\blur0.3\fs14\fnComic Sans MS\c&H97E0CC&\3c&HDAFFF1&\b0\frz35.81\pos(37.5,158)}shining
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:05:01.61,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(479,1)\blur0.3\bord1.5\fnGeorgia\c&H97E0CC&\3c&HDAFFF1&\frz332.3\pos(391.5,55.5)}Trendy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:05:01.61,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(479,1)\blur0.3\bord1.5\fnGeorgia\c&H97E0CC&\3c&HDAFFF1&\frz32\pos(67,52)}Trendy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:05:01.61,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(479,1)\blur0.3\fs14\fnComic Sans MS\c&H97E0CC&\3c&HDAFFF1&\b0\frz330.5\pos(517,40)}smells so good
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.61,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a movie, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:05.61,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, we have to figure out \Nour T-shirt design for the concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:08.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than just wearing whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.35,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't having matching outfits
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,create a sense of one-ness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,A sense of band-ness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.62,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(441,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs18\b1\c&H3844BE&\3c&HD1DEE8&\bord1.5\pos(519,178.5)}Ripe Mangos
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:15.62,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.59,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing tying you guys together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.46,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I know that's what {\i1}she'll{\i0} say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.74,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You get it? We're not here to play around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.13,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:31.22,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnTimes New Roman\bord2\c&H000000&\3c&H4A4A4A&}Welcome to Chez Gotoh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:36.16,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. I'll put it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, we could play around a {\i1}little{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.27,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'd love that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.35,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well then, I'll fetch the drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.47,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Please make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:47.86,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:53.66,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But wow, she really went \Nall-out with the decorations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:57.22,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here besides the guitar \Nand effects unit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.29,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:02.17,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I just assumed her room would have \Na bit more of a rock feel to—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:10.05,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(402,1)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H010301&\3c&H595959&\pos(322.5,304)\fay-0.18}Sealed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.67,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... rock? 🤨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's pretty rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:13.11,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I w-wonder if there's \Nanything else rock about i—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.10,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:18.94,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Bruh? Why does she have so \Nmany copies of our ProPho?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.69,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs18\c&H010301&\3c&H595959&\frz350\pos(318.5,23.5)}Sealed {\3c&H1E534F&\frz10}Sealed {\3c&H595959&\frz335}Sealed
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.69,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs18\c&H010301&\3c&H423132&\frz10\pos(322,19.5)}Sealed {\3c&H423132&\frz330}Sealed {\3c&H1E534F&\frz310}Sealed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:28.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, \Nbut it seems pretty darn rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.45,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,She's got blown-up ones too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:37.54,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,342)\an8\fnTimes New Roman\bord2\c&H000000&\3c&H4A4A4A&}Welcome to Chez Gotoh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:34.50,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,She had this picture stuck up \Nall over her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.30,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,She said she really liked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:42.20,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,But Mom told her to take them down\Nbecause they were hurting her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:47.42,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,And we put those seals up \Nwhen Sis was possessed before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.84,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,That should just about cover it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.80,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you Gotoh-san's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.48,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! A pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.30,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Futari Gotoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.73,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,The dog's Jimihen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I hope barley tea's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:08.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Or would they prefer a trendier drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.57,Default,Nijika/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.54,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you guys wa—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.95,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, will you play the \NMunions song on guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.80,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'll practice so I can do it \Nthe next time I come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.00,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta! When's the next time you come by?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.29,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.46,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Jimihen's a friendly little guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:31.42,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're getting along so well, \Nthere's no room left for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:34.80,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A five-year-old and a dog \Nhave better social skills than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.49,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Sis is frozen up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:42.00,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,F-Futari. Wh-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.25,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where are Mom and Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.45,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:48.71,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I've got grown-up things to talk about, \Nso please go play with Jimihen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.04,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.56,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind having Futari-chan here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.61,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, same!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.20,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:59.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I c-c-can't whoop it up if my sister's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:02.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, you've been \Nwhooping it up with us all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.28,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.33,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Please go play with Jimihen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.14,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You can have an ice pop from the freezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:13.92,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.90,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You've got such a sisterly bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get that\Nfrom what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:24.67,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's design those T-shirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.48,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,1)\shad2\bord4\fnComic Sans MS\fs28\c&H0B36B5&\3c&HEFF3F5&\4c&H863D5B&\pos(108,81)\frz19.18}L{\c&HC85918&}e{\c&H9784F6&}t{\c&H4FA91A&}'{\c&H6785E8&}s {\c&H1C42BA&}D{\c&HC85918&}r{\c&H9784F6&}a{\c&H4FA91A&}w
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.48,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to use these!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.85,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:28.46,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We could just slap\Nour logo on there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:33.57,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd love to sell the shirts as merch, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.12,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nijika-chan is so hungry for merch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:39.54,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So if you have any other great ideas, \NI might use those as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.01,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's do our best, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.25,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.89,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I have to impress the others for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:49.42,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, take that stuff off \Nbefore you try to look serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.16,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,What? They really came?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.47,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Really? fr?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:54.74,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,fr!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.83,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,These friends aren't just the imaginary kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:58.64,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,fr fr!
