Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:11.53,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(525,1)\blur0.4\fnComic Sans MS\fs24\c&H1C0E16&\pos(329.5,133)}Kessoku\NBand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:11.53,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(525,1)\blur0.4\fnComic Sans MS\fs14\c&H1C0E16&\pos(270,220)}Together,\Nlet's seize\Nthe flower\Nof victory!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.83,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The concept is friendship, \Neffort, and victory!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.53,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a dang sports festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:14.30,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, but I think it's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on. What are we winning at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how "victory" \Napplies to a concert...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.62,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Um... vibes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.53,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Vibes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:24.91,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I just think wearing these would \Nreally get us feeling like a unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.16,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Gotoh-sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.02,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Class unity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:30.63,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.66,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Is the idea of a sports festival \Nthat traumatic for you?!
