Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.92,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A heinous ritual in which those \Nwith no athletic ability are shunned,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:46.69,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and even their right to exist \Nis stripped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.06,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Not only during school hours, \Nbut afterward too,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:53.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,they are forced to perform slave labor, \Ncreating banners and practicing cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:58.41,DefaultTop,Classmates,0000,0000,0000,,One for all! All for one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:04.12,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs30\bord2\an8\c&H00099F&\3c&H0439B5&\pos(323,119)}Class Unity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:03.51,DefaultTop,Classmates,0000,0000,0000,,One for all! All for one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:06.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,An entire month's torturous existence \Nliving for naught but the sports festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:08.62,DefaultTop,Classmates,0000,0000,0000,,One for all! All for one!
