Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.88,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Gotoh-san melted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.94,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is hot today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:27.18,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.3\fs12\fnTimes New Roman\c&H171F7B&\pos(412.5,117)}This way to\NSchool Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:35.15,DefaultTop,Classmates,0000,0000,0000,,No cooperation, no life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:30.94,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But the true terror lurking \Nbehind every sports festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:41.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this week's Bocchi Time lasted \Nthrough the whole commercial break!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.47,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:46.32,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You've really put your foot\N in it now, Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:49.12,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What? Come back, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:58.59,DefaultTop,Classmates,0000,0000,0000,,No cooperation, no life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:53.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A place in which introverts \Nare constantly underfoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:54.92,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but if they just sit quietly in a corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:58.59,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,they're persecuted for \Nnot being team players!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.41,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Death to those who bring down \Nthe sports festival mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.47,Default,Classmates,0000,0000,0000,,No cooperation, no life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.02,Default,Classmates,0000,0000,0000,,No cooperation, no life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.98,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,See? They really exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:16.93,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:19.15,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.62,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.66,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined Hitori \Nwould have real friends over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.48,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Eat your fill, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:27.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.66,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.15,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,You let Hitori join your band, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:31.75,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.35,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't exactly "let" her join.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:36.69,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her to join, and she \Nwas willing to humor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.26,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,See? Music really brings people together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:43.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Jimihen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:47.76,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't cause too much trouble with her \Nretreats into her own little world, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:50.77,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, that's no trouble at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.55,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.68,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Here, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:59.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I'm still\Nupset about school festivals
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:01.79,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,makes me realize I'm a downer even more,\Nwhich made everything worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:03.99,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Karaage's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.17,Default,Nijika/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.62,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,That one is soy sauce with garlic,\Nand this one is shio koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.37,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,And there's lemon and \Nshichimi spice to taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:14.15,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.17,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.29,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,When she said she had friends coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:22.98,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed they were imaginary \Nor hallucinations,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:24.52,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,but then, she did have that picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.86,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hallucinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:29.89,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, image editing software \Nis pretty sophisticated these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:30.85,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Software?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:35.00,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,If I might ask, you're not from \Nsome kind of friend rental servi—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.43,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're her bona fide bandmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:38.88,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it doesn't sound \Nlike something I'd do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:42.32,DefaultTop,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that Hitori's never \Nbrought a friend home before.{bg}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:44.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but hearing Mom and Dad's \Nideas about me is so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:47.38,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So Bocchi's like this even at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:51.95,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,She's been so restless for days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.58,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,She said something about practicing \Ndecorating her room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:59.30,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,put it all up, took it all down, \Nand put it back up, over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:04.47,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,And she played a simulated game of Twister, \Njust in case you played.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.43,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mom! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.97,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell them all that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.68,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we went shopping just in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.54,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this is a day worth remembering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.83,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,A friend-a-versary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.82,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Friend-a-versity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:20.23,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:24.20,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NThe job she said she'd gotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's at my sister's club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan mainly serves \Ndrinks to customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.37,Default,Michiyo/Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,T-To customers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.30,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:35.18,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It does feel pretty weird to \Nhave friends at my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.38,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:37.69,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. Music really does \Ncause personal growth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:41.80,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,And you were having so much fun \Nwhen we burst in like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:42.61,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.51,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should butt out?
