Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.68,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.72,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:59.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That's my favorite heartwarming movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.11,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to watch that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.62,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna watch it all together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.25,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.93,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea! What fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:14.54,DefaultTop,Naoki/Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! So fun! So fun! Yeah!
