Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:42.04,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We still need to design \Nour T-shirts for the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.15,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait...
