Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:01.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan! We're running \Nout of time! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:05.21,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-An ordinary girl has two hot \Nguys trying to win her heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.76,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.64,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:09.10,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But if someone that cute is "ordinary," \Nwhat hope is there for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.31,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo sent in a bunch of design ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:14.10,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see! I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Look with us, Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.64,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.44,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:28.74,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Now sushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.15,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
