Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan, don't actually respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.93,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bocchi-chan's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.12,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:52.63,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might like to see my design...
