Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.00,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.94,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,S-So cringe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.49,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it too trendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:19.16,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's that mystery font I see on bottom text memes all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.02,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would keep people focused \Non our clothing when we're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:25.13,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for several reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.38,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of all \Nthe zippers and chains?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.20,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could use \Nthe zippers to hold picks,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:32.30,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and the chain could serve \Nas a guitar strap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.51,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Weirdly practical!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.83,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,So, can I assume we're all in on this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.97,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.79,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you like to wear normally?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:46.88,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My mom buys my clothes, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.30,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.42,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've never worn any of them, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They're not to my taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:55.64,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:58.45,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Same! I've never seen you in \Nanything but the tracksuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, please! Try one on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:03.50,Default,Nijika/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:07.88,Default,Nijika/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please! Please! \NPlease! Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.85,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:12.74,Default,Nijika/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:17.95,Default,Nijika/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:24.30,Default,Nijika/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.30,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I love it! Look right this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:28.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No pictures, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! Bocchi-chan is drippin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.03,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to forget, with how she usually is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.14,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... c-can I take it off now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.57,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:41.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's brush back your bangs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:44.16,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.51,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Are you growing them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:48.42,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I j-just can't get to the salon, \Nso they grow out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.38,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do some styling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.97,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:17.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan's turning into Hiroshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:22.20,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Her body can't keep up with the sudden \Nstress of her face being exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.82,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan's... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:37.90,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to find a new guitarist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.76,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm suddenly so dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:50.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The room is so damp all of a sudden, \Nlike all the air's been sucked out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:53.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I breathed it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.89,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,S-So did I!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:00.54,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no use. G-Going limp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:05.45,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... Gotoh-san's curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.98,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Would anyone like dessert?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.46,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,We've got the sweets Kita-chan brought—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:22.51,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for trying to push \Nthrough everything with positivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:25.51,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't get good at guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:27.77,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being too cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.02,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,They're all acting like Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.00,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, the salt and the seals!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.52,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Should I call that exorcist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.94,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(104,1)\an7\bord2\fs8\c&H000000&\3c&HA2A5A3&\frz348.3\pos(415,129.5)}Nijika\N You'll have to do the concert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:39.96,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.57,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,290)}Several Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:43.57,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.93,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Since nobody had any good ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.62,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,we're going with my T-shirt design!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.13,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.71,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(654,1)\fnImpact\c&HC7CDC7&\pos(316.5,194.5)}Kessoku Band
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:51.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.11,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make this, Ijichi-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:56.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty good at the design stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:59.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you just \Ndesign it from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:00.97,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:07.97,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you were just thinking,\N"Then why didn't you just design it from the start?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's psychic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:17.61,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad2\bord4\fnComic Sans MS\fs28\c&H0B36B5&\3c&HEFF3F5&\4c&H863D5B&\pos(335.5,86)\frz76.51}L{\c&HC85918&}e{\c&H9784F6&}t{\c&H4FA91A&}'{\c&H6785E8&}s {\c&H1C42BA&}D{\c&HC85918&}r{\c&H9784F6&}a{\c&H4FA91A&}w
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:17.61,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting pretty good at\Nguessing what you're thinking lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:20.91,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Our ties feel so much stronger now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:23.36,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:25.46,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,The quality of the model helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:27.37,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8\fnImpact\c&HCCCDCA&\frz180\pos(315.5,120)\frx30}Kessoku Band
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:26.79,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:29.12,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, look right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:34.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Two days to our concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And we worked hard to make our ties feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.61,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, looks like there's a typhoon on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,No way! This is the first I've heard of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:45.67,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Summer weather is so fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.33,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:49.14,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But what about the concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.89,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Should we make rain charms?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.07,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's our only choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:57.41,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Your quota is ten each!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:58.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:01.25,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it looks like it won't\Nhit the Kanto region, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, that's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.77,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:07.39,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:10.19,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I think the new song's coming \Ntogether pretty well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.36,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:12.54,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're all sounding awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:16.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:22.30,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shouldn't we still make the \Nrain charms? Just to be safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:26.01,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure! Better safe than sorry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.20,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring in what we need to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.98,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:34.56,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't made rain charms \Nsince elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:37.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to being negative, \Nso I always assume the worst, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.02,DefaultTop,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, the five younger brothers \NI haven't seen since birth—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.81,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting above it! It was your idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:40.35,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.03,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.03,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8\fnImpact\c&HCCCDCA&\frz180\frx30\pos(315.5,113)}Kessoku Band
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:49.35,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:55.87,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord1.5\fs9\c&H6BFAE8&\3c&H449F90&\pos(358.5,33)}Course Changed to Make Landfall\NLook Out for Strong Winds and Heavy Rain
