Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:55.87,DefaultItalics,Weatherman,0000,0000,0000,,Typhoon #8 has taken an unexpected course...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.96,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.3\fs40\fnImpact\pos(320,200)\c&H23F9FA&}DAY OF THE CONCERT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:21.42,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,I sleep, with big problems \Nweighing down on me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:32.08,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you can't beat that feeling \Nof being loved, it's true
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:41.76,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,When I awaken from cold dreams, \Nmy body feels numb
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:50.50,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,You shine so brightly, \Nit could make me a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:55.38,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to take that step
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:23:03.10,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,Though there's nothing certain about it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:10.23,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It carries my childish heart into tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:14.60,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to blast out the thoughts \Nrattling around in my brain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:17.18,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,And live, to its fullest, a life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:22.16,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been taking advances on for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:24.67,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,But I also love the days I spend \Nlying around, doing nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.29,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,So I know I'm going to go see you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:33.09,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,Before it all disappears some day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3572,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H41403D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\bord2\shad2\4c&H07C4F3&\pos(309,49.5)}#08 Bocchi the Rock
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:39.98,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!
